stream
BT
/F1 12 Tf
72 760 Td
14 TL
(REFLASHING GUIDE) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(DIY ELRS ESP32-C3 Zero Receiver) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Use this guide when you want to reflash the custom receiver firmware later.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Every Time You Reflash) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Step 1) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Open the project in VS Code:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(File -> Open Folder -> E:\\expresslrsc3\\ExpressLRS\\src) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Step 2) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Open the terminal:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Ctrl + ~) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Step 3) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Plug in the ESP32-C3 Zero by USB.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Case A: Reflash Firmware Only) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Use this if you only changed the binding phrase or other build flags and do not need to) Tj
T*
(refresh the filesystem.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(powershell) Tj
T*
(pio run -e DIY_ESP32C3_Zero_SX1281_2400_RX_via_UART --target upload) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Case B: Reflash Everything) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Use this after a fresh clone, after major config changes, or if the board crashes on) Tj
T*
(boot.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(First flash the filesystem:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(powershell) Tj
T*
(pio run -e DIY_ESP32C3_Zero_SX1281_2400_RX_via_UART --target uploadfs) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Wait for SUCCESS, then flash firmware:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(powershell) Tj
T*
(pio run -e DIY_ESP32C3_Zero_SX1281_2400_RX_via_UART --target upload) Tj
ET
endstream
