() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If Upload Gets Stuck At Connecting) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Hold the BOOT button on the board.) Tj
T*
(2. Run the upload command.) Tj
T*
(3. Release the button when Connecting... appears.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Verify It Worked) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Wait about 60 seconds after flashing.) Tj
T*
(2. On your phone, connect to the receiver WiFi.) Tj
T*
(3. SSID: ExpressLRS RX) Tj
T*
(4. Password: expresslrs) Tj
T*
(5. Open: http://10.0.0.1) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Expected result:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- The page should load successfully.) Tj
T*
(- The firmware target should show DIY_ESP32C3_ZERO_SX1281_2400_RX.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Change Binding Phrase) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Open src/user_defines.txt and edit:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(text) Tj
T*
(-DMY_BINDING_PHRASE="your-phrase-here") Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Then do a full reflash:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- uploadfs) Tj
T*
(- upload) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Recommended Habit) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If you are not sure whether only firmware is enough, do the full reflash sequence:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. uploadfs) Tj
T*
(2. upload) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(That is the safest option for this custom target.) Tj
ET
